tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE phishing_campaigns (
  campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  success_rate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE phishing_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    campaign_start_date DATE,
    campaign_end_date DATE,
    total_emails_sent INT
);

CREATE TABLE phishing_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT REFERENCES phishing_campaigns(campaign_id),
    recipient_email TEXT,
    opened BOOLEAN,
    clicked BOOLEAN,
    reported BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE phishing_campaigns (
    campaign_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    success_rate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE emails (
    email_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID,
    recipient_email VARCHAR(255),
    opened BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE links (
    link_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    email_id UUID,
    link_url VARCHAR(255),
    clicked BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE statistics (
    stat_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID,
    email_id UUID,
    link_id UUID,
    open_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    click_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE phishing_campaigns (
    campaign_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    target_url VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_metrics (
    metric_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID REFERENCES phishing_campaigns(campaign_id),
    open_rate FLOAT,
    click_rate FLOAT,
    conversion_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE email_logs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID REFERENCES phishing_campaigns(campaign_id),
    email_address VARCHAR(255),
    sent_date TIMESTAMP,
    opened BOOLEAN,
    clicked BOOLEAN,
    converted BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE link_clicks (
    click_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    log_id UUID REFERENCES email_logs(log_id),
    link_url VARCHAR(255),
    click_date TIMESTAMP,
    clicked_by_email BOOLEAN
);
